Post-Upgrade Tasks for Insurance

To complete your upgrade, perform required post-upgrade tasks.

Activate and Deploy LWC OmniScripts
Assign Custom Object Permissions for Data Mapper Bundles and Data Mapper Map Items
Create and Activate Lightning Record Pages for Insurance
Edit Page Layout Assignments for Insurance
Assign Permission Set Licenses for Insurance Industries Extension Objects
Verify and Update Required Permissions for Quoting
Required Permissions for the Partner Community User Profile
Field-Level Security Permission Set for Fields on the Quote Object
Automatic Vlocity State Transition Component Refresh
Field-Level Security Permission Set for Insurance Industries Extension Objects and Fields in Upgrades
Complete Post-Install Steps for Contract Lifecycle Management for Insurance
Set Up User Access with Insurance Permission Sets
Harmonize Your Insurance Org
Build Insurance Product Models
Build Rating Procedures
Create Quotes
Track Commissions
Manage Insurance Policies
Manage Claims
Manage Group Benefits
title: Post-Upgrade Tasks for Salesforce Insurance
